>4 in all\nnine Planck channels, 75 of which are found outside the Planck mask adopted\nhere. The remaining 76 sources inside the Galactic mask are very likely\nGalactic objects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Feb 2018 17:27:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Sep 2018 12:12:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-14"}
