ve 10-100 times slower than in\nmixtures with oxygen; the higher the percentage of methane, the faster the\nfronts move.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Feb 2018 20:56:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Feb 2019 18:14:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-14"}
